logicalColumns.name: Average Discount
logicalColumns.description:
converted from attribute17 of the order header.
If original value is empty or equals 'Total list price amount equal 0' - this field will show 0.

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 = 'Total list price amount equal 0' THEN 0 ELSE  CAST ( IFNULL(%1, 0) AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) END

logicalColumns.name: Average Discount (Varchar)
logicalColumns.description:
Sourced from attribute17 of the order header
contains also the String value "Total list price amount equal 0"

logicalColumns.name: Order Channel
logicalColumns.description:
Order Header.Attribute7 
This refers to "Direct Indirect Deal"

expressionObjects: logicalColumn:SSYS_SF.Dim - Sale Order Header.Order Creation DateTime

logicalColumns.name: Order Or Quote
logicalColumns.description:
Quote = If "Order Number" is empty
Sales Order = If "Order Number" is not empty

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 IS NULL  THEN 'Quote' ELSE 'Sales Order' END

logicalColumns.name: Order Type - Group
logicalColumns.description:
CASE WHEN "Header Details"."Order Type Name" like ('Standard%') THEN 
  'Standard Order' 
when "Header Details"."Order Type Name" like ('Trade%') THEN 
  'Trade In Order' 
when "Header Details"."Order Type Name" like ('Lease %') then
   'Lease Order' 
ELSE "Header Details"."Order Type Name" END

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 LIKE 'Standard\%' THEN 'Standard Order' WHEN %1 LIKE 'Trade\%' THEN 'Trade In Order' WHEN %1 LIKE 'Lease \%' THEN 'Lease Order' ELSE %1 END

logicalColumns.name: Average Discount Calc
logicalColumns.description:
Calculated average discount per order header
as defined in EBS custom function :xxar_autoinvoice_pkg.view_average_discount

logicalColumns.name: Average Discount Multiplier
logicalColumns.description:
If "Average Discount" Is 100 : value will be 0.
else, value will be (100-"Average Discount")/100

logicalColumns.name: Header Discount Auto Adjustments
logicalColumns.description: sum all order's adjustments with type='discount' done automatically at ORDER level

logicalColumns.name: Header Discount Manual Adjustments
logicalColumns.description: sum all order's adjustments with type='discount' done manually at ORDER level
